             was indicted for <rs id="t17910413-44-off246" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910413-44-off246" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910413-44-off246" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously making an assault, on the King's highway, on 
                     <persName id="t17910413-44-victim549" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Charlton
                     <interp inst="t17910413-44-victim549" type="surname" value="Charlton"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17910413-44-victim549" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17910413-44-victim549" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , on the <rs id="t17910413-44-cd247" type="crimeDate">26th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-44-off246 t17910413-44-cd247"></join>, putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, one man's hat, value 8 s.
            </rs> the goods and chattels of 
               <persName id="t17910413-44-victim550" type="victimName">
                  Thomas and 
                        
                           <persName id="t17910413-44-victim552" type="victimName">
                              James 
                              Ivory
